---
title: Beef Tenderloin & Creamy Truffle Polenta with Crunchy Roasted Broccoli, Shallot Sauce & Parmesan
description: Enjoy a restaurant-quality meal any night of the week with this sumptuous dinner. You’ll pair juicy seared beef tenderloins with creamy truffle and Parmesan polenta that cooks up in a flash. Roasted broccoli with crispy panko breadcrumbs is a perfect side, and a homemade shallot pan sauce makes for a luxe finishing touch.

